message.body: Do u know of any free things to do in Philly with the kids?
I'm sure there's gotta be stuff but its hard to think of stuff off the top of my head cause I haven't done stuff like that in a long time. What kinda stuff do they like to do/want to do...??
Well it's kinda hard cause there all different ages. But we will do anything. Idk either
I'll.try to think of something. The internet might have something. ...or I can check the local city papers.
I checked online but thought mayb u would know of some other stuff. Thanks anyway. They just want to do expensive stuff. I'm a baller on a budget.
I feel ya. If they want to go paintballing I can find some pretty sweet deals.
Oh wow that sounds good. I'll let u know
